{"tha-ap397:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap397:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap397:0.3":"5 Padumakutagariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap397:1.1":"“Piyadassi nama bhagava, ","tha-ap397:1.2":"sayambhu lokanayako; ","tha-ap397:1.3":"Vivekakamo sambuddho, ","tha-ap397:1.4":"samadhikusalo muni. ","tha-ap397:2.1":"Vanasandam samogayha, ","tha-ap397:2.2":"piyadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap397:2.3":"Pamsukulam pattharitva, ","tha-ap397:2.4":"nisidi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap397:3.1":"Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap397:3.2":"aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap397:3.3":"Pasadam migamesanto, ","tha-ap397:3.4":"ahindami aham tada. ","tha-ap397:4.1":"Tatthaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap397:4.2":"oghatinnamanasavam; ","tha-ap397:4.3":"Pupphitam salarajamva, ","tha-ap397:4.4":"sataramsimva uggatam. ","tha-ap397:5.1":"Disvanaham devadevam, ","tha-ap397:5.2":"piyadassim mahayasam; ","tha-ap397:5.3":"Jatassaram samogayha, ","tha-ap397:5.4":"padumam aharim tada. ","tha-ap397:6.1":"Aharitvana padumam, ","tha-ap397:6.2":"satapattam manoramam; ","tha-ap397:6.3":"Kutagaram karitvana, ","tha-ap397:6.4":"chadayim padumenaham. ","tha-ap397:7.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap397:7.2":"piyadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap397:7.3":"Sattarattindivam buddho, ","tha-ap397:7.4":"kutagare vasi jino. ","tha-ap397:8.1":"Puranam chaddayitvana, ","tha-ap397:8.2":"navena chadayim aham; ","tha-ap397:8.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap397:8.4":"atthasim tavade aham. ","tha-ap397:9.1":"Vutthahitva samadhimha, ","tha-ap397:9.2":"piyadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap397:9.3":"Disam anuvilokento, ","tha-ap397:9.4":"nisidi lokanayako. ","tha-ap397:10.1":"Tada sudassano nama, ","tha-ap397:10.2":"upatthako mahiddhiko; ","tha-ap397:10.3":"Cittamannaya buddhassa, ","tha-ap397:10.4":"piyadassissa satthuno. ","tha-ap397:11.1":"Asitiya sahassehi, ","tha-ap397:11.2":"bhikkhuhi parivarito; ","tha-ap397:11.3":"Vanante sukhamasinam, ","tha-ap397:11.4":"upesi lokanayakam. ","tha-ap397:12.1":"Yavata vanasandamhi, ","tha-ap397:12.2":"adhivattha ca devata; ","tha-ap397:12.3":"Buddhassa cittamannaya, ","tha-ap397:12.4":"sabbe sannipatum tada. ","tha-ap397:13.1":"Samagatesu yakkhesu, ","tha-ap397:13.2":"kumbhande saharakkhase; ","tha-ap397:13.3":"Bhikkhusanghe ca sampatte, ","tha-ap397:13.4":"gatha pabyahari jino. ","tha-ap397:14.1":"‘Yo mam sattaham pujesi, ","tha-ap397:14.2":"avasanca akasi me; ","tha-ap397:14.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap397:14.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap397:15.1":"Sududdasam sunipunam, ","tha-ap397:15.2":"gambhiram suppakasitam; ","tha-ap397:15.3":"Nanena kittayissami, ","tha-ap397:15.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap397:16.1":"Catuddasani kappani, ","tha-ap397:16.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap397:16.3":"Kutagaram mahantassa, ","tha-ap397:16.4":"padmapupphehi chaditam. ","tha-ap397:17.1":"Akase dharayissati, ","tha-ap397:17.2":"Pupphakammassidam phalam; ","tha-ap397:17.3":"Catubbise kappasate, ","tha-ap397:17.4":"Vokinnam samsarissati. ","tha-ap397:18.1":"Tattha pupphamayam byamham, ","tha-ap397:18.2":"Akase dharayissati; ","tha-ap397:18.3":"Yatha padumapattamhi, ","tha-ap397:18.4":"Toyam na upalimpati. ","tha-ap397:19.1":"Tathevimassa nanamhi, ","tha-ap397:19.2":"kilesa nopalimpare; ","tha-ap397:19.3":"Manasa vinivattetva, ","tha-ap397:19.4":"panca nivarane ayam. ","tha-ap397:20.1":"Cittam janetva nekkhamme, ","tha-ap397:20.2":"agara pabbajissati; ","tha-ap397:20.3":"Tato pupphamaye byamhe, ","tha-ap397:20.4":"dharente nikkhamissati. ","tha-ap397:21.1":"Rukkhamule vasantassa, ","tha-ap397:21.2":"Nipakassa satimato; ","tha-ap397:21.3":"Tattha pupphamayam byamham, ","tha-ap397:21.4":"Matthake dharayissati. ","tha-ap397:22.1":"Civaram pindapatanca, ","tha-ap397:22.2":"paccayam sayanasanam; ","tha-ap397:22.3":"Datvana bhikkhusanghassa, ","tha-ap397:22.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap397:23.1":"Kutagarena carata, ","tha-ap397:23.2":"pabbajjam abhinikkhamim; ","tha-ap397:23.3":"Rukkhamule vasantampi, ","tha-ap397:23.4":"kutagaram dhariyati. ","tha-ap397:24.1":"Civare pindapate ca, ","tha-ap397:24.2":"cetana me na vijjati; ","tha-ap397:24.3":"Punnakammena samyutto, ","tha-ap397:24.4":"labhami parinitthitam. ","tha-ap397:25.1":"Gananato asankheyya, ","tha-ap397:25.2":"kappakoti bahu mama; ","tha-ap397:25.3":"Rittaka te atikkanta, ","tha-ap397:25.4":"pamutta lokanayaka. ","tha-ap397:26.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap397:26.2":"piyadassi vinayako; ","tha-ap397:26.3":"Tamaham payirupasitva, ","tha-ap397:26.4":"imam yonim upagato. ","tha-ap397:27.1":"Idha passami sambuddham, ","tha-ap397:27.2":"anomam nama cakkhumam; ","tha-ap397:27.3":"Tamaham upagantvana, ","tha-ap397:27.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap397:28.1":"Dukkhassantakaro buddho, ","tha-ap397:28.2":"maggam me desayi jino; ","tha-ap397:28.3":"Tassa dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap397:28.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap397:29.1":"Tosayitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap397:29.2":"gotamam sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap397:29.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap397:29.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap397:30.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap397:30.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap397:30.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap397:30.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap397:31.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap397:31.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap397:31.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap397:31.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap397:32.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap397:32.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap397:32.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap397:33.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap397:33.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap397:33.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap397:34.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma padumakutagariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap397:35.1":"Padumakutagariyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}